explanation: The loop 'for j in range(i):' only iterated j values smaller than i, so the program missed valid comparisons where the potentially superior product has a smaller index (j > i). I changed that line to iterate all products ('for j in range(n):'); comparing an item with itself cannot satisfy the strict condition, so no extra checks are needed.
